{
  "stem": "18102.5",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we stayed there through December of 1940.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So it was something over a year that we lived in Vilna.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there were two portions of time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In the beginning, when the Lithuanians were the governing power of Vilna, he lived with us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We got an apartment, a one-- sort of one room apartment overlooking [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's interesting I mentioned [INAUDIBLE] because [INAUDIBLE] ended up to be on the street on which the headquarters of the uprising of the ghetto eventually was there, only a few doorways, in fact from where we lived on [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] was deep within the Jewish quarter, of course, of Vilna.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was actually the butcher's street, so that, you know, during the normal times, this was a hub of activity which butcher shops and people coming, and milling, and buying, and-- and so forth.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we lived on-- on the second floor overlooking this street with a little balcony that I would stand in front of from time to time.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The circumstances were a little different though, because now suddenly, instead of learning Polish, I was learning Lithuanian.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So this was my actual third language in my seven and a half years of life, Yiddish, Polish, and now Lithuanian.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it was more or less normal.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was with kids my age, kids on the street.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I-- I learned the facts of life.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I, I had friends.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had birthday parties.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And while we were refugees, the community took us in because my parents are well-known, respected individuals.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we immediately became part of the social sphere of Jewish life in Vilna.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But that only lasted until the Russians changed their mind, took back not only Vilna, but all of Lithuania, as you know.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And suddenly, my father was on the lam again.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
